<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Georama Drama"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="ジオラマドラマ"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Isekaijoucho"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="ヰ世界情緒"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="异世界情绪"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Creation"/><amll:meta key="album" value="創生"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="JPZ922014599"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="1907752032"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="002Tom0x1ugWsy"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="336304144"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="0Efg6AeuEjIyvYwbbu989i"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1688352885"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="174598250"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="ASyunagi"/></metadata></head><body dur="2:45.600"><div begin="14.360" end="2:45.600"><p begin="14.360" end="20.620" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="14.360" end="15.000">愛</span><span begin="15.000" end="15.270">想</span><span begin="15.270" end="15.880">笑</span><span begin="15.880" end="16.000">い</span><span begin="16.000" end="17.700">が</span><span begin="18.250" end="18.460">上</span><span begin="18.460" end="18.660">手</span><span begin="18.660" end="18.840">く</span><span begin="18.840" end="19.050">な</span><span begin="19.050" end="19.220">っ</span><span begin="19.220" end="20.620">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">渐渐擅长挤出敷衍的笑</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">漸漸擅長擠出敷衍的笑</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Getting better at forced smiles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">겉치레 웃음이 능숙해져서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je deviens meilleure pour les faux sourires</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Me he vuelto mejor fingiendo sonrisas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das erzwungene Lächeln fällt mir immer leichter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tornando-me boa em sorrir por conveniência</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я стала лучше притворно улыбаться</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sono diventata brava con i sorrisi forzati</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aisowarai ga umaku natte</span></p><p begin="21.120" end="24.100" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="21.120" end="21.320">狡</span><span begin="21.320" end="21.520">猾</span><span begin="21.520" end="21.760">く</span><span begin="21.760" end="21.930">な</span><span begin="21.930" end="22.090">っ</span><span begin="22.090" end="22.950">て</span><span begin="22.950" end="23.160">い</span><span begin="23.160" end="24.100">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">也慢慢变得圆滑狡黠</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">也慢慢變得圓滑狡黠</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Becoming more cunning</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">점점 교활해져 가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et je deviens de plus en plus rusée</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y me voy volviendo más astuta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich werde immer listiger</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vou ficando cada vez mais astuta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И становлюсь всё хитрее</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E divento sempre più scaltra</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Zuruku natte iku</span></p><p begin="25.850" end="31.140" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="25.850" end="26.210">し</span><span begin="26.210" end="26.570">が</span><span begin="26.570" end="26.900">な</span><span begin="26.900" end="27.290">い</span><span begin="27.290" end="28.720">末</span><span begin="28.720" end="29.030">路</span><span begin="29.030" end="29.440">を</span> <span begin="29.750" end="29.970">踏</span><span begin="29.970" end="30.150">み</span><span begin="30.150" end="30.380">締</span><span begin="30.380" end="31.140">め</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">踩着微不足道的末路</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">踩著微不足道的末路</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Treading firmly upon a miserable end</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">보잘것없는 말로를 딛고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Foulant aux pieds une fin misérable</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Pisando fuerte este final insignificante</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auf das unbedeutende Ende tretend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Pisando firme em um fim insignificante</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ступая по своему жалкому финалу</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Calpestando una fine miserevole</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shiganai matsuro o fumishime</span></p><p begin="31.560" end="35.580" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="31.560" end="32.280">確</span><span begin="32.280" end="32.680">か</span><span begin="32.680" end="33.040">め</span><span begin="33.040" end="33.400">て</span><span begin="33.400" end="33.760">る</span><span begin="34.050" end="34.480">よ</span><span begin="34.480" end="34.650">う</span><span begin="34.650" end="35.580">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">仿佛在反复确认什么</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">彷彿在反覆確認什麼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">As if confirming it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">확인하는 듯한</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Comme pour m&apos;en assurer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Como si estuviera asegurándome</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Als würde ich mich vergewissern</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Como se estivesse confirmando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Словно пытаясь в чём-то убедиться</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Come per averne la conferma</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tashikameteru you na</span></p><p begin="36.070" end="38.550" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="36.070" end="36.280">あ</span><span begin="36.280" end="36.520">な</span><span begin="36.790" end="37.000">た</span><span begin="37.000" end="37.210">が</span><span begin="37.500" end="37.670">く</span><span begin="37.670" end="37.880">れ</span><span begin="37.880" end="38.060">た</span><span begin="38.060" end="38.230">の</span><span begin="38.230" end="38.550">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你曾赠予我的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你曾贈予我的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">What you gave me was</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">당신이 준 것은</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce que tu m&apos;as offert</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Lo que tú me diste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Was du mir gabst war</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O que você me deu foi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">То что ты подарил мне</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ciò che tu mi hai donato</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Anata ga kureta no wa</span></p><p begin="38.770" end="41.490" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="38.770" end="38.970">あ</span><span begin="38.970" end="39.140">の</span><span begin="39.140" end="39.810">小</span><span begin="39.810" end="40.410">さ</span><span begin="40.410" end="40.550">な</span><span begin="40.550" end="40.940">箱</span><span begin="40.940" end="41.490">庭</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">是那座小小的袖珍庭院</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">是那座小小的袖珍庭院</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">That small miniature garden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그 작은 모형 정원</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">C&apos;est ce petit jardin miniature</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Fue aquel pequeño jardín en miniatura</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Jenes kleine Miniaturgärtchen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Aquele pequeno jardim em miniatura</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Тот маленький сад в коробке</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">È quel piccolo giardino in miniatura</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ano chiisana hakoniwa</span></p><p begin="41.490" end="46.210" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="41.490" end="41.660">触</span><span begin="41.660" end="41.820">れ</span><span begin="41.820" end="42.020">た</span><span begin="42.020" end="42.690">ら</span> <span begin="43.080" end="43.830">崩</span><span begin="43.830" end="44.170">れ</span><span begin="44.170" end="44.530">落</span><span begin="44.530" end="44.850">ち</span><span begin="44.850" end="45.970">そ</span><span begin="45.970" end="46.210">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">稍一碰触 便似要崩塌散落</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">稍一碰觸 便似要崩塌散落</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Seemingly about to crumble if touched</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">닿으면 무너져 내릴 것 같아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Qui semble prêt à s&apos;effondrer au moindre contact</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si lo toco parece que se derrumbará</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn man es berührt scheint es zu zerfallen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se eu tocar parece que vai desmoronar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Кажется он рассыплется если коснусь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sembra sul punto di crollare se lo sfioro</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Furetara kuzureochisou</span></p><p begin="47.760" end="49.980" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="47.760" end="48.090">演</span><span begin="48.090" end="48.300">じ</span><span begin="48.300" end="48.500">て</span> <span begin="48.680" end="49.020">僕</span><span begin="49.020" end="49.190">は</span><span begin="49.190" end="49.500">演</span><span begin="49.500" end="49.740">じ</span><span begin="49.740" end="49.980">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我扮演着 不停扮演着</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我扮演著 不停扮演著</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Acting, I am acting</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">연기하며 나는 연기하며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Jouant un rôle, je joue mon rôle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Actuando yo actuando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich spiele ich spiele meine Rolle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Interpretando eu vou interpretando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Играя я продолжаю играть</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Recito io recito</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Enjite boku wa enjite</span></p><p begin="50.090" end="52.630" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="50.090" end="50.450">深</span><span begin="50.450" end="50.620">く</span><span begin="50.620" end="50.990">臙</span><span begin="50.990" end="51.170">脂</span><span begin="51.170" end="51.540">の</span><span begin="51.540" end="52.630">糸</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">殷红如胭脂的丝线</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">殷紅如胭脂的絲線</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Deep carmine threads</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">짙은 연지색 실</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un fil d&apos;un carmin profond</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Un hilo de un profundo carmesí</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein tiefer karmesinroter Faden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O fio de um carmim profundo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Глубокие карминовые нити</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Un profondo filo color cremisi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Fukaku enji no ito</span></p><p begin="53.070" end="56.350" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="53.070" end="54.810">唇</span> <span begin="54.900" end="55.300">絡</span><span begin="55.300" end="55.490">ま</span><span begin="55.490" end="55.720">る</span><span begin="55.810" end="56.180">言</span><span begin="56.180" end="56.350">葉</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">唇齿间 是纠缠不清的言语</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">唇齒間 是糾纏不清的言語</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Words tangled at my lips</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">입술에 얽히는 말들</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Sur mes lèvres, des mots s&apos;entremêlent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Palabras que se enredan en mis labios</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Worte die sich um meine Lippen schlingen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Lábios palavras emaranhadas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Слова запутавшиеся на губах</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sulle labbra parole intrecciate</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kuchibiru karamaru kotoba</span></p><p begin="56.360" end="59.250" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="56.360" end="56.750">僕</span><span begin="56.750" end="56.910">だ</span><span begin="56.910" end="57.170">け</span><span begin="57.280" end="57.470">の</span><span begin="57.470" end="57.810">色</span> <span begin="57.810" end="58.050">画</span><span begin="58.050" end="58.220">を</span> <span begin="58.220" end="58.690">描</span><span begin="58.690" end="58.910">く</span><span begin="58.910" end="59.060">の</span><span begin="59.060" end="59.250">さ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我要画出 只属于我的色彩与图景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我要畫出 只屬於我的色彩與圖景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Drawing colors and pictures that are mine alone</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나만의 색으로 그림을 그리는 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je dessine un tableau aux couleurs qui n&apos;appartiennent qu&apos;à moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Pintaré un cuadro con mis propios colores</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein Bild in nur meinen Farben malen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vou pintar as cores e imagens só minhas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я нарисую картину в своих собственных цветах</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dipingo un quadro con i miei soli colori</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Boku dake no iro e o egaku no sa</span></p><p begin="59.250" end="1:04.470" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="59.250" end="59.620">断</span><span begin="59.620" end="59.790">じ</span><span begin="59.790" end="59.990">て</span><span begin="1:00.150" end="1:00.490">甘</span><span begin="1:00.490" end="1:00.680">く</span><span begin="1:00.680" end="1:00.990">賛</span><span begin="1:00.990" end="1:01.230">辞</span><span begin="1:01.230" end="1:01.400">を</span><span begin="1:01.590" end="1:01.960">贈</span><span begin="1:01.960" end="1:02.150">る</span><span begin="1:02.150" end="1:02.320">共</span><span begin="1:02.320" end="1:02.500">演</span><span begin="1:02.500" end="1:02.680">者</span><span begin="1:02.680" end="1:02.960">は</span><span begin="1:03.210" end="1:03.510">亡</span><span begin="1:03.510" end="1:04.470">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">绝不会有同伴 献上廉价的赞美</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">絕不會有同伴 獻上廉價的讚美</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Without any co-stars to offer sweet praise</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">결단코 달콤한 찬사를 보낼 공연자는 없고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Il n&apos;y a absolument aucun partenaire pour m&apos;offrir de douces louanges</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sin coprotagonistas que den elogios dulces con determinación</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es gibt keine Mitspieler die mir süßes Lob schenken</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Certamente não há coadjuvantes que ofereçam doces elogios</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Нет партнёров по сцене что одарят решительной и сладкой похвалой</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non ci sono attori che offrano dolci lodi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Danjite amaku sanji o okuru enja wa naku</span></p><p begin="1:04.580" end="1:07.180" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:04.580" end="1:05.000">こ</span><span begin="1:05.000" end="1:05.280">の</span><span begin="1:05.540" end="1:05.810">役</span><span begin="1:05.810" end="1:06.090">名</span><span begin="1:06.090" end="1:06.250">は</span><span begin="1:06.250" end="1:06.620">借</span><span begin="1:06.620" end="1:06.810">り</span><span begin="1:06.810" end="1:07.180">物</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">就连这角色的名字 也是借来的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">就連這角色的名字 也是借來的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">This role name is a borrowed thing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 배역의 이름은 빌려온 것</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce nom de scène n&apos;est qu&apos;un emprunt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El nombre de este papel es prestado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dieser Name meiner Rolle ist nur geborgt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Este nome do papel é emprestado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Имя этой роли взято взаймы</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il nome di questo ruolo è preso in prestito</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kono namae wa karimono</span></p><p begin="1:07.350" end="1:10.320" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:07.350" end="1:07.520">い</span><span begin="1:07.520" end="1:07.690">つ</span><span begin="1:07.690" end="1:07.870">か</span><span begin="1:07.870" end="1:08.240">最</span><span begin="1:08.240" end="1:08.430">期</span><span begin="1:08.430" end="1:08.680">の</span><span begin="1:08.790" end="1:09.190">刻</span><span begin="1:09.190" end="1:09.330">を</span><span begin="1:09.330" end="1:09.690">待</span><span begin="1:09.690" end="1:09.860">っ</span><span begin="1:09.860" end="1:10.320">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">静静等待着 终末时刻的降临</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">靜靜等待著 終末時刻的降臨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Waiting for the final moment someday</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">언젠가 최후의 순간을 기다리며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Attendant un jour l&apos;instant ultime</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Esperando algún día el momento final</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Irgendwann auf den letzten Augenblick wartend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Esperando algum dia pelo momento final</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Когда-нибудь дождавшись последнего часа</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">In attesa dell&apos;ultimo istante un giorno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Itsuka saigo no toki o matte</span></p><p begin="1:10.760" end="1:20.760" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:10.760" end="1:12.130">正</span><span begin="1:12.130" end="1:12.670">し</span><span begin="1:12.880" end="1:13.360">い</span><span begin="1:13.550" end="1:14.120">台</span><span begin="1:14.120" end="1:14.700">詞</span><span begin="1:14.700" end="1:15.130">で</span> <span begin="1:16.490" end="1:17.850">正</span><span begin="1:17.850" end="1:18.250">し</span><span begin="1:18.640" end="1:19.030">く</span><span begin="1:19.030" end="1:19.650">愛</span><span begin="1:19.650" end="1:20.090">し</span><span begin="1:20.090" end="1:20.450">て</span><span begin="1:20.450" end="1:20.760">ね</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">用正确的台词 好好地爱我吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">用正確的台詞 好好地愛我吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">With the right lines, love me correctly okay</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">올바른 대사로 올바르게 사랑해 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Avec les bonnes répliques, aime-moi comme il se doit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ámame correctamente con el guion correcto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Liebe mich bitte mit den richtigen Worten auf die richtige Weise</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Com as falas certas me ame corretamente viu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Люби же меня правильно говоря правильные слова</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Con le battute giuste amami correttamente</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tadashii serifu de tadashiku aishite ne</span></p><p begin="1:23.250" end="1:32.290" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:23.250" end="1:24.010">物</span><span begin="1:24.010" end="1:24.940">語</span><span begin="1:24.940" end="1:26.770">は</span> <span begin="1:28.970" end="1:29.810">進</span><span begin="1:29.810" end="1:29.980">む</span><span begin="1:29.980" end="1:30.450">ば</span><span begin="1:30.450" end="1:30.890">か</span><span begin="1:30.890" end="1:31.250">り</span><span begin="1:31.250" end="1:32.290">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">故事只会一味地向前推进</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">故事只會一味地向前推進</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The story only keeps moving forward</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이야기는 나아갈 뿐이라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">L&apos;histoire ne fait que progresser</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La historia no hace más que avanzar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Geschichte schreitet nur immerfort voran</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A história apenas segue em frente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">История лишь продолжает идти вперёд</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La storia non fa altro che avanzare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Monogatari wa susumu bakari de</span></p><p begin="1:34.760" end="1:40.130" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:34.760" end="1:35.190">し</span><span begin="1:35.190" end="1:35.550">が</span><span begin="1:35.550" end="1:35.920">な</span><span begin="1:35.920" end="1:36.220">い</span><span begin="1:36.220" end="1:37.670">最</span><span begin="1:37.670" end="1:38.020">期</span><span begin="1:38.020" end="1:38.550">を</span><span begin="1:38.790" end="1:39.150">恐</span><span begin="1:39.150" end="1:39.330">れ</span><span begin="1:39.330" end="1:40.130">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">畏惧着微不足道的结局</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">畏懼著微不足道的結局</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Fearing a miserable end</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">보잘것없는 최후를 두려워하며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Craignant une fin misérable</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Temiendo un final insignificante</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das unbedeutende Ende fürchtend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Temendo o fim insignificante</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Боясь своего жалкого конца</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Temendo una fine miserevole</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shiganai saigo o osorete</span></p><p begin="1:40.490" end="1:44.680" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:40.490" end="1:40.770">張</span><span begin="1:40.770" end="1:41.280">り</span><span begin="1:41.280" end="1:41.640">付</span><span begin="1:41.640" end="1:42.000">く</span><span begin="1:42.000" end="1:42.390">ペ</span><span begin="1:42.390" end="1:43.010">ル</span><span begin="1:43.010" end="1:43.620">ソ</span><span begin="1:43.620" end="1:44.680">ナ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">紧紧依附的假面 无法剥离</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">緊緊依附的假面 無法剝離</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">A persona sticking fast</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">달라붙어 떨어지지 않는 페르소나</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Cette persona qui reste collée à moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Mi persona está adherida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Persona die fest an mir klebt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A persona que está grudada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Приросшая маска которую не снять</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La maschera rimasta incollata</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Haritsuku perusona</span></p><p begin="1:45.010" end="1:47.510" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:45.010" end="1:45.250">こ</span><span begin="1:45.250" end="1:45.470">の</span><span begin="1:45.780" end="1:46.310">歌</span><span begin="1:46.310" end="1:46.480">が</span><span begin="1:46.480" end="1:46.850">示</span><span begin="1:46.850" end="1:47.040">す</span><span begin="1:47.040" end="1:47.220">も</span><span begin="1:47.220" end="1:47.510">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这首歌所昭示的一切</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這首歌所昭示的一切</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">What this song indicates</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 노래가 나타내는 것</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce que cette chanson indique</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Lo que esta canción muestra</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Was dieses Lied offenbart</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O que esta canção indica</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">То на что указывает эта песня</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ciò che questa canzone indica</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kono uta ga shimesu mono</span></p><p begin="1:47.740" end="1:50.340" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:47.740" end="1:48.120">僕</span><span begin="1:48.120" end="1:48.320">が</span><span begin="1:48.620" end="1:48.820">詰</span><span begin="1:48.820" end="1:49.180">め</span><span begin="1:49.180" end="1:49.350">た</span><span begin="1:49.350" end="1:49.740">思</span><span begin="1:49.740" end="1:50.090">惑</span><span begin="1:50.090" end="1:50.340">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">还有我藏在其中的心思</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">還有我藏在心中的心思</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The intentions I&apos;ve packed inside</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내가 채워 넣은 속셈을</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les intentions que j&apos;y ai enfermées</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las intenciones que he guardado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Absichten die ich hineingelegt habe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">As intenções que eu guardei</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Те замыслы что я в неё вложила</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Le intenzioni che ho racchiuso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Boku ga tsumeta omowaku o</span></p><p begin="1:50.620" end="1:55.870" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:50.620" end="1:50.830">あ</span><span begin="1:50.830" end="1:51.000">な</span><span begin="1:51.000" end="1:51.350">た</span><span begin="1:51.350" end="1:51.670">が</span><span begin="1:51.670" end="1:52.090">知</span><span begin="1:52.090" end="1:52.450">る</span><span begin="1:52.450" end="1:53.170">由</span><span begin="1:53.170" end="1:53.500">も</span><span begin="1:53.500" end="1:53.890">な</span><span begin="1:53.890" end="1:54.740">い</span><span begin="1:54.940" end="1:55.120">で</span><span begin="1:55.120" end="1:55.210">し</span><span begin="1:55.210" end="1:55.680">ょ</span><span begin="1:55.680" end="1:55.870">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你大概 从来都不曾知晓吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你大概 從來都不曾知曉吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">You probably have no way of knowing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">당신이 알 리 없겠지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu n&apos;as sûrement aucun moyen de les connaître n&apos;est-ce pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Seguramente no tienes forma de saberlo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Du wirst wohl keine Möglichkeit haben sie zu kennen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você provavelmente não tem como saber não é?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Тебе наверняка никогда не узнать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Probabilmente non avrai modo di saperlo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Anata ga shiru yoshi mo nai deshou</span></p><p begin="1:56.540" end="1:59.040" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:56.540" end="1:57.100">曖</span><span begin="1:57.260" end="1:57.800">昧</span><span begin="1:57.990" end="1:58.160">な</span><span begin="1:58.160" end="1:58.430">身</span><span begin="1:58.430" end="1:58.710">体</span><span begin="1:58.710" end="1:59.040">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">模糊的身躯</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">模糊的身軀</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">This ambiguous body</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">애매한 신체는</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce corps ambigu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Mi cuerpo ambiguo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mein verschwommener Körper</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O corpo vago</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Моё призрачное тело</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il corpo ambiguo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aimai na karada wa</span></p><p begin="1:59.240" end="2:01.870" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:59.240" end="1:59.590">空</span><span begin="1:59.590" end="1:59.980">に</span><span begin="2:00.100" end="2:00.850">宙</span><span begin="2:00.850" end="2:01.020">に</span> <span begin="2:01.020" end="2:01.420">解</span><span begin="2:01.420" end="2:01.580">れ</span><span begin="2:01.580" end="2:01.870">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在半空之中 渐渐松散 瓦解</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在半空之中 漸漸鬆散 瓦解</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Unraveling into the sky and air</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">허공 속에서 풀려나</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">S&apos;effiloche dans les airs, dans le vide</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Se deshilacha en el aire en el espacio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Löst sich in der Leere des Himmels auf</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">No céu no ar desfazendo-se</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Распутывается и тает в пустоте</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Si scioglie nel vuoto e nel cielo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kuu ni chuu ni hogurete</span></p><p begin="2:02.130" end="2:06.840" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:02.130" end="2:02.480">今</span><span begin="2:02.480" end="2:03.190">に</span><span begin="2:03.520" end="2:04.320">崩</span><span begin="2:04.320" end="2:04.650">れ</span><span begin="2:04.650" end="2:05.000">落</span><span begin="2:05.000" end="2:05.370">ち</span><span begin="2:05.370" end="2:06.580">そ</span><span begin="2:06.580" end="2:06.840">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">此刻仿佛 下一秒就要崩塌</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">此刻彷彿 下一秒就要崩塌</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Seemingly about to crumble at any moment</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">금방이라도 무너져 내릴 것 같아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Prêt à s&apos;effondrer d&apos;un instant à l&apos;autre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Siento que va a derrumbarse ahora mismo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Scheint jeden Moment in sich zusammenzufallen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Parece que vai desmoronar a qualquer momento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Кажется оно вот-вот рассыплется</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sembra sul punto di crollare proprio ora</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ima ni kuzureochisou</span></p><p begin="2:09.560" end="2:11.850" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:09.560" end="2:09.990">演</span><span begin="2:09.990" end="2:10.220">じ</span><span begin="2:10.220" end="2:10.480">て</span> <span begin="2:10.580" end="2:10.940">僕</span><span begin="2:10.940" end="2:11.120">は</span><span begin="2:11.120" end="2:11.410">演</span><span begin="2:11.410" end="2:11.640">じ</span><span begin="2:11.640" end="2:11.850">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我扮演着 不停扮演着</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我扮演著 不停扮演著</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Acting, I am acting</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">연기하며 나는 연기하며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Jouant un rôle, je joue mon rôle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Actuando yo actuando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich spiele ich spiele meine Rolle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Interpretando eu vou interpretando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Играя я продолжаю играть</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Recito io recito</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Enjite boku wa enjite</span></p><p begin="2:12.000" end="2:14.570" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:12.000" end="2:12.360">深</span><span begin="2:12.360" end="2:12.550">く</span><span begin="2:12.550" end="2:12.880">臙</span><span begin="2:12.880" end="2:13.100">脂</span><span begin="2:13.100" end="2:13.460">の</span><span begin="2:13.460" end="2:14.570">糸</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">殷红如胭脂的丝线</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">殷紅如胭脂的絲線</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Deep carmine threads</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">짙은 연지색 실</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un fil d&apos;un carmin profond</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Un hilo de un profundo carmesí</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein tiefer karmesinroter Faden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O fio de um carmim profundo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Глубокие карминовые нити</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Un profondo filo color cremisi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Fukaku enji no ito</span></p><p begin="2:15.030" end="2:18.300" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:15.030" end="2:16.800">唇</span> <span begin="2:16.800" end="2:17.230">絡</span><span begin="2:17.230" end="2:17.410">ま</span><span begin="2:17.410" end="2:17.630">る</span><span begin="2:17.720" end="2:18.120">言</span><span begin="2:18.120" end="2:18.300">葉</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">唇齿间 是纠缠不清的言语</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">唇齒間 是糾纏不清的言語</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Words tangled at my lips</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">입술에 얽히는 말들</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Sur mes lèvres, des mots s&apos;entremêlent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Palabras que se enredan en mis labios</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Worte die sich um meine Lippen schlingen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Lábios palavras emaranhadas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Слова запутавшиеся на губах</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sulle labbra parole intrecciate</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kuchibiru karamaru kotoba</span></p><p begin="2:18.300" end="2:21.140" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:18.300" end="2:18.660">僕</span><span begin="2:18.660" end="2:18.820">だ</span><span begin="2:18.820" end="2:19.090">け</span><span begin="2:19.200" end="2:19.390">の</span><span begin="2:19.390" end="2:19.730">色</span> <span begin="2:19.730" end="2:19.950">画</span><span begin="2:19.950" end="2:20.130">を</span> <span begin="2:20.130" end="2:20.600">描</span><span begin="2:20.600" end="2:20.820">く</span><span begin="2:20.820" end="2:20.980">の</span><span begin="2:20.980" end="2:21.140">さ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我要画出 只属于我的色彩与图景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我要畫出 只屬於我的色彩與圖景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Drawing colors and pictures that are mine alone</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나만의 색으로 그림을 그리는 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je dessine un tableau aux couleurs qui n&apos;appartiennent qu&apos;à moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Pintaré un cuadro con mis propios colores</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein Bild in nur meinen Farben malen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vou pintar as cores e imagens só minhas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я нарисую картину в своих собственных цветах</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dipingo un quadro con i miei soli colori</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Boku dake no iro e o egaku no sa</span></p><p begin="2:21.140" end="2:23.310" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:21.140" end="2:21.520">案</span><span begin="2:21.520" end="2:21.700">じ</span><span begin="2:21.700" end="2:21.920">て</span><span begin="2:22.060" end="2:22.460">覆</span><span begin="2:22.460" end="2:22.580">う</span><span begin="2:22.580" end="2:22.970">惨</span><span begin="2:22.970" end="2:23.160">事</span><span begin="2:23.160" end="2:23.310">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">将令人担忧的 覆满阴霾的惨事</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">將令人擔憂的 覆滿陰霾的慘事</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The catastrophe covered in anxiety</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">걱정하며 뒤덮는 참극을</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Couvrant le désastre inquiétant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La tragedia que cubro preocupada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die besorgniserregende Tragödie verdeckend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A tragédia que cubro por preocupação</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Все эти тревожные бедствия</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Coprendo il disastro che mi preoccupa</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Anjite oou sanji o</span></p><p begin="2:23.500" end="2:26.250" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:23.500" end="2:23.700">エ</span><span begin="2:23.700" end="2:23.880">ン</span><span begin="2:23.880" end="2:24.060">ド</span><span begin="2:24.060" end="2:24.300">ロ</span><span begin="2:24.300" end="2:24.540">ー</span><span begin="2:24.540" end="2:24.770">ル</span><span begin="2:24.770" end="2:24.990">に</span><span begin="2:24.990" end="2:25.230">載</span><span begin="2:25.230" end="2:25.480">せ</span><span begin="2:25.480" end="2:26.250">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">全都印在片尾的滚动字幕里</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">全都印在片尾的滾動字幕裡</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Putting it in the end roll</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">엔드롤에 실어서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pour le faire figurer au générique de fin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Poniéndola en los créditos finales</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sie im Abspann erscheinen lassend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Colocando nos créditos finais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я оставлю в финальных титрах</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mettendolo nei titoli di coda</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Endorooru ni nosete</span></p><p begin="2:26.530" end="2:29.090" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:26.530" end="2:26.930">こ</span><span begin="2:26.930" end="2:27.240">の</span><span begin="2:27.460" end="2:27.670">役</span><span begin="2:27.670" end="2:28.010">名</span><span begin="2:28.010" end="2:28.170">は</span><span begin="2:28.170" end="2:28.540">借</span><span begin="2:28.540" end="2:28.720">り</span><span begin="2:28.720" end="2:29.090">物</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">就连这角色的名字 也是借来的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">就連這角色的名字 也是借來的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">This role name is a borrowed thing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 배역의 이름은 빌려온 것</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce nom de scène n&apos;est qu&apos;un emprunt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El nombre de este papel es prestado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dieser Name meiner Rolle ist nur geborgt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Este nome do papel é emprestado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Имя этой роли взято взаймы</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il nome di questo ruolo è preso in prestito</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kono namae wa karimono</span></p><p begin="2:29.260" end="2:32.070" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:29.260" end="2:29.440">い</span><span begin="2:29.440" end="2:29.620">つ</span><span begin="2:29.620" end="2:29.800">か</span><span begin="2:29.800" end="2:30.140">最</span><span begin="2:30.140" end="2:30.340">期</span><span begin="2:30.340" end="2:30.680">の</span><span begin="2:30.680" end="2:31.070">刻</span><span begin="2:31.070" end="2:31.260">を</span><span begin="2:31.260" end="2:31.510">待</span><span begin="2:31.510" end="2:31.760">っ</span><span begin="2:31.760" end="2:32.070">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">静静等待着 终末时刻的降临</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">靜靜等待著 終末時刻的降臨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Waiting for the final moment someday</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">언젠가 최후의 순간을 기다리며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Attendant un jour l&apos;instant ultime</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Esperando algún día el momento final</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Irgendwann auf den letzten Augenblick wartend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Esperando algum dia pelo momento final</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Когда-нибудь дождавшись последнего часа</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">In attesa dell&apos;ultimo istante un giorno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Itsuka saigo no toki o matte</span></p><p begin="2:32.290" end="2:34.930" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:32.290" end="2:32.680">こ</span><span begin="2:32.680" end="2:32.880">の</span><span begin="2:33.210" end="2:33.480">人</span><span begin="2:33.480" end="2:33.750">生</span><span begin="2:33.750" end="2:33.920">を</span><span begin="2:33.920" end="2:34.480">還</span><span begin="2:34.480" end="2:34.650">し</span><span begin="2:34.650" end="2:34.930">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">把这短暂的人生 归还回去</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">把這短暫的人生 歸還回去</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Returning this life</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 인생을 돌려주고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">En rendant cette vie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Devolviendo esta vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dieses Leben zurückgebend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Devolvendo esta vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Верни мне эту жизнь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Restituendo questa vita</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kono subete o kaeshite</span></p><p begin="2:34.980" end="2:39.800" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:34.980" end="2:35.190">そ</span><span begin="2:35.190" end="2:35.360">の</span><span begin="2:35.360" end="2:35.700">時</span> <span begin="2:35.700" end="2:36.330">心</span><span begin="2:36.440" end="2:36.620">か</span><span begin="2:36.620" end="2:36.820">ら</span><span begin="2:36.820" end="2:37.350">笑</span><span begin="2:37.350" end="2:37.530">い</span><span begin="2:37.530" end="2:37.950">た</span><span begin="2:37.950" end="2:38.070">い</span><span begin="2:38.070" end="2:38.440">だ</span><span begin="2:38.440" end="2:39.800">け</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">只盼望那时 能从心底真正笑一次</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">只盼望那時 能從心底真正笑一次</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">At that time I just want to laugh from the heart</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그때 마음껏 웃고 싶을 뿐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux seulement pouvoir rire de tout mon cœur à ce moment-là</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En ese momento solo quiero reír de corazón</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">In jenem Moment möchte ich einfach nur von Herzen lachen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Naquela hora só quero sorrir de coração</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В тот миг я просто хочу рассмеяться от всего сердца</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio solo sorridere dal cuore in quel momento</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono toki kokoro kara waraitai dake</span></p><p begin="2:43.810" end="2:45.600" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:43.810" end="2:44.170">だ</span><span begin="2:44.170" end="2:45.600">け</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">仅此而已</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">僅此而已</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Just that</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그뿐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Seulement</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Solo eso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Einfach nur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Apenas isso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И только</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Solo questo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dake</span></p></div></body></tt>